        <div class="col-md-12">
          <p class='description'>
            Our company grew out of a frustration from watching some asset management companies making what some may consider exorbitant profits while acting in a manner that may be against the best interests of their investors. BlackVault Investments is an investment management firm startup out of Silicon Valley, that in true Silicon Valley fashion, aims to bring ethics and morality into the finance industry. We recognize the importance of manager-investor relationships and the need for them to be a good fit for each other. It is because of this that we are very selective in choosing our investors. We believe in making sure our investors are as comfortable as possible, and we do everything we can to make the on-boarding process as smooth as possible. Once on board, investors can directly contact our investment professionals. Our goal is to protect assets even during the harshest economic or market conditions. Additionally, our strategy does not look at specific sectors or markets and is not localized to a certain country or region. Instead, it looks for value across all corners of the globe from developed markets such as the United States and Europe to emerging markets such as China and India.
          </p>
