            <h2>Investment Process</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12 mg-bt-80 athelas">
          <p>
            We live in an ever-evolving world where markets are dynamic and expanding. To compensate for this, we put full faith in strategy execution and controlling the variables that are in our control. Our strategy focuses solely on value and fundamental analysis. We believe that long-run returns are best achieved through the robust selection of companies that are trading at low valuations. We consider top and bottom fundamental analysis on all of our investment decisions that involve thorough due diligence. Our in-depth process ensures that each name in our portfolio is fully vetted, and tracked enabling our team to execute entry and exit points to conserve our investor's capital. We believe our sole focus on value provides us with the advantage to buy when others are selling and sell when others are buying.
          </p>
        </div>
